   *   code 404 :  (Not Found)
   *   code 500 :  (Internal Server Error)
   * 
   * Available security schemes:
   *   GatewayLogin (apiKey)
   *   DirectLogin (apiKey)
   * 
   * @param consumerid The CONSUMERID identifier
   */
